N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 189.1 - Use of "u.s." prefix

State Regulations

In describing or marking lettuce, packed or repacked within
this State and offered for sale on a graded basis the letters "U.S." may be
prefixed to any of the grade terms, and when so prefixed the lettuce to which
they relate shall be regarded as represented as graded according to New York
official lettuce grades. Notes
